claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A partial view of the first page of a clinical research article titled “Recombinant or Standard-Dose Influenza Vaccine in Adults under 65 Years of Age,” listing the authors and showing the beginning of the abstract section.
